Module imagingbook.parboiled.examples.java

module imagingbook.parboiled.examples.java
This is a modularized version of the parboiled PEG parser Java/Scala implementation originally developed by Mathias Doenitz, refactored from https://github.com/sirthias/parboiled (Version 1.4.1, Jan. 2023).
